<figureCitation box="[159,266,1805,1830]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–9" captionStartId="6.[151,264,1589,1612]" captionTargetBox="[311,1285,457,1517]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[234,1353,375,1565]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURES 1–9. Baiocis species males. 1‒3. B. crassiventris. 1, dorsal view; 2, lateral view head; 3, lateral view elytral apex. 4. B. anaticeps, lateral view elytral apex. 5‒6. B. perinimicus, elytral apex. 5, posterolateral view; 6, lateral view. 7‒8. B. incisus. 7, dorsal view elytral apex; 8, ventral view abdomen. 9. B. spiniventris, ventral view abdomen. Scale line = 1.0 mm (Fig. 1); 0.5 mm (Figs 2‒6, 9); 0.67 mm (Figs 7‒8)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1292273/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="483">Figs. 1‒3</figureCitation>
